name: cryptochristo - ode to joy tape speed distortion
description:
Joy, beautiful spark of gods,
Daughter of Elysium,
We enter, drunk with fire,
Heavenly one, thy sanctuary!
Thy magic binds again
What custom strictly divided
All people become brothers,
Where thy gentle wing abides.
If Christ rises, it will be in Crypto Sancte. Praise the mint.

@floresfeias - synth, sequencer and tape solist
@blusimonwasem - volca, tapes, bass and electroacoustic projections
